---
title: Laksa-Style Tofu & Prawn Noodle Soup with Asian Greens
description: Settle in for a cosy night with this hearty tofu, prawn noodle soup. Full of colourful veggies, slurpable noodles and Southeast Asian
flavours, this is the perfect meal to warm you up on a cold night!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/666b8db4f6d6f122b49fdd5a-43f4bd2f.jpeg
